<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://web.archive.org/web/20091028180701/http:/geocities.com/Athens/Forum/5037/sapir.html">The Function of an International Auxiliary Language</a> — An article written by linguist <a href="Edward_Sapir" title="Edward Sapir">Edward Sapir</a> discussing the need for prospects of an international language.</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.rickharrison.com/language/farewell.html">Farewell to auxiliary languages</a>, a criticism of the auxiliary language movement by Richard K. Harrison.</li>
